        <mxCell id="9" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#1d4ed8&quot;&gt;1&lt;/font&gt; &amp;nbsp; sender source&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;monospace&quot;&gt;trice8C(&quot;cmd:setLeds&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;&amp;amp;mask, 1);&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dbeafe;strokeColor=#38bdf8;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=16;fontColor=#1f2937;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
